{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f81c42cf9e","title":"在宪法公布后的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b7c6925bf8","index":0,"year":1954,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"f81c42cf9e"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3766d87da7","name":"革命大批判","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1949.10-1957.12）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd.pdf"},{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3448cc11cb","type":"paragraph","text":"宪法草业公布时的话讲（记亲稿）","index":0,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"f81c42cf9e"},{"id":"a1f3e0f5ad","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五四年六月）","index":1,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"f81c42cf9e"},{"id":"0be967622b","type":"paragraph","text":"、怡当地正确地总了经脸，反帝反封建革命的经险；建国以后各方面建设的经脸；同时又总结了反面的经验（历史上各种宪法），并且总结了外国的经，但以自己民族的经龄为主，瓷产阶极有革命的东西，也不能全部否定。","index":2,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"f81c42cf9e"},{"id":"26cc5c20a0","type":"paragraph","text":"二、怡当地正确地粘合了原即性与灵活性。民主主义与社会主义原则贯彻在各方面。灵活性，统--战线，逐步实行。不逐步就“左”，不实行，就右，社会主义的原则性与逐步实行的灵活性相粘合。少数民族有他的共同性和特殊性，根据特殊情况制定单行条例。","index":3,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"f81c42cf9e"},{"id":"a37aa66879","type":"paragraph","text":"宪法可以实行，而且必须实行，尤其是国家工作人员，不实行，要弹动（共产党员犯罪，要开除党籍）。有了宪法，全国人民就有了清楚而正确的道路，这是全国人民的总章程。这在国际上还发生很大的影响，宪法有民族性，又有国际性。","index":4,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"f81c42cf9e"},{"id":"ce69c29b97","type":"paragraph","text":"究竟要多少年进人社会主义，这不要死了，十五年只能打一个基础。团黏全国人民，团箱一切可以团黏的力量。","index":5,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"f81c42cf9e"},{"id":"33b12ab394","type":"paragraph","text":"国家主席的权好象太小了。有些条女没有写进去，并不是逊，而是不科学。科学，多了也不行，少了也不行，敲多少就多少。对古人今人都不能迷信，对了就信，不对就不信，我们不提倡崇拜偶象。","index":6,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"f81c42cf9e"},{"id":"07b4a97724","type":"paragraph","text":"在宪法公布后的指示","index":7,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"f81c42cf9e"},{"id":"7d39e5cac6","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五四年六月）","index":8,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"f81c42cf9e"},{"id":"981c80cca5","type":"paragraph","text":"我何要剂正镇导上的机会主义，官主义蜡，革命人民一定要有请愿、要工、黑课的自由，我们是社会主义阶段，还要前进！颁导上有蜡允许人民公开批帮聊！小字报、大字报、大融、大批判都是很好的形式。","index":9,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"f81c42cf9e"},{"id":"f9bfd3bd7a","type":"paragraph","text":"在阿尔巴尼亚大使吴递国书时的答词","index":10,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"f81c42cf9e"},{"id":"7923f3048c","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五四年九月十三日）大使同志：","index":11,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"f81c42cf9e"},{"id":"664ad1ab53","type":"paragraph","text":"我非常愉快地接受您所呈递的阿尔巴尼亚人民共和国人民会主席团任命您为驻中华","index":12,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"f81c42cf9e"}],"page":{"id":"8a9c21697a","publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"f81c42cf9e","start":52,"end":52}},"maoquanji34":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b306b52039","type":"title","text":"在宪法公布后的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"f81c42cf9e"},{"id":"ca5e2873b9","type":"paragraph","text":"我们要纠正领导上的机会主义、官主义错误，革命人民一定要有请愿、黑工、黑课的自由，我们是社会主义阶段，还要前进嘛！领导上有错误允许人民公开批评嘛，小字报、大学报、大辩论、天批判都是很好的形式","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"f81c42cf9e"}],"page":{"id":"c4d622eabf","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"f81c42cf9e","start":147,"end":147}}}},"__N_SSG":true}